# @arc/ui only

Business code imports UI from `@arc/ui` only — never directly from `heroui-native`, `heroui-native-pro`, `react-native-safe-area-context`, `lucide-react-native`, `@gorhom/*`, `@dicebear/*`.

Layer decision tree (ADR 006): OSS primitive → Pro primitive → wrapper → navigation → finance → charts → avatar. See `CLAUDE.md` §五.

Gain/loss colors: `packages/ui/tokens/semantic.ts` — no hard-coded hex for up/down.
